promote your opportunities, as well as to increase knowledge of the organization itself to students.  In addition to Career Fairs, Information Sessions, and Information Tables, additional student engagement opportunities include the following options:       IP   Industry Panels  This is an opportunity to serve on an industry panel to provide students information about specific industries, occupational opportunities, and trends. If you are interested in being part of any future programs we will offer, please let us know!       SV   Site Visits  These are generally comprised of providing students an opportunity to visit your organization for a tour of your setting. This could also include a panel presentation and/or overview information session at your site.       TO   Targeted Outreach  Our Employer Relations Team can provide assistance with targeted outreach to students via listservs, student organizations, other events, advertising opportunities, and more!  Purchase an Ad  Employers can take out Ads in our Annual Career Planning Guide and Job Fair Guides . Ads work to maximize the visibility of your organization on UIC’s campus and attract top talent to your opportunities.       Info   Need More Information?  The Employer Relations Team would be happy to tell you more about our great students, academic programs offered here at UIC, demographics, and discuss what recruiting options work best for your organization and employment needs. At your convenience, we can visit you at your office or you are always welcome to meet us here at UIC!       Your UIC Employer Relations Team:      Jaime
    
